<div class="container">
  <div class="banner">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6 column-text">
        <h1>Don't waste time chasing your dreams. Just use it to do them.</h1>
        <p>- The Bucket List Team</p>
        <%= link_to "Start Here!", buckets_path, class: "blue-button large-button space-between" %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-5 column-images">
        <div>
          <div class="card-image">
            <div class="show-info">From the confort of your home create your Bucket List!</div>
            <%= image_tag "sofa.png", class: "image" %>
          </div>
          <div class="card-image">
            <div class="show-info">Find the hottest deals on the activities you added to your Bucket List!</div>
            <%= image_tag "hot-deals.png", class: "image" %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="card-image">
            <div class="show-info">Add the activities that you would love to do, but, never had the  money and/or found the perfect time for it.</div>
            <%= image_tag "heart.png", class: "image" %>
          </div>
          <div class="card-image">
            <div class="show-info">And most important of all. SAVE MONEY. You can add budgets to your activities.</div>
            <%= image_tag "saving-money.png", class: "image" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row mt-5">
    <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-10 column-text center-home-page-content">
      <h2 class="title2">What are the top 10 bucket list items?</h2>
      <p>Items that are closer to your budget will appear at the top, and, if they meet the budget will appear with a highlight.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="activity-perimetre col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-10 center-home-page-content">
      <div class="card-activity">
        <div class="activity-image" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.2),rgba(0,0,0,0.2)), url(<%= asset_path "love.jpg" %>);"></div>
        <div class="card-activity-infos">
          <h2>Fall in love</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="activity-offer-price green">83%</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="activity-perimetre col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-10 center-home-page-content">
      <div class="card-activity">
        <div class="activity-image" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.2),rgba(0,0,0,0.2)), url(<%= asset_path "wine.jpg" %>);"></div>
        <div class="card-activity-infos">
          <h2>Go on a wine tour in Napa</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="activity-offer-price orange">53%</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="activity-perimetre col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-10 center-home-page-content">
      <div class="card-activity">
        <div class="activity-image" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.2),rgba(0,0,0,0.2)), url(<%= asset_path "health.jpg" %>);"></div>
        <div class="card-activity-infos">
          <h2>Get to my ideal weight</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="activity-offer-price orange">51%</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="activity-perimetre col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-10 center-home-page-content">
      <div class="card-activity">
        <div class="activity-image" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.2),rgba(0,0,0,0.2)), url(<%= asset_path "safari.jpg" %>);"></div>
        <div class="card-activity-infos">
          <h2>Go on a safari</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="activity-offer-price red">45%</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="activity-perimetre col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-10 center-home-page-content">
